uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-hands-on-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-hands-on-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-hands-on-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/marvels-spider-man-2">《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》</a></em>中彼得·帕克的扮演者尤里·洛文塔尔 (Yuri Lowenthal) 透露，他试图“尽可能地”让<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel">漫威</a>义务警员月亮骑士加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/insomniac-games">Insomniac Games</a>的续集中。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/marvels-spider-man-2-review-3513197">《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》评论：超级英雄游戏的新标准</a></strong></li></ul><p>作为<em>漫威《蜘蛛侠 2》</em>创意总监<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-bryan-intihar-marvels-spider-man-2-3516664">Bryan Intihar Boss 级别简介的</a>一部分，洛文塔尔告诉<em>NME</em> ，他经常缠着导演在游戏中加入超自然反英雄月亮骑士。</p><p> “他忍受了我对月亮骑士的痴迷，月亮骑士是我试图在每次谈话中塞进的另一个漫威角色，”洛文塔尔分享道。 “我尝试过让《月光骑士》尽可能多地融入游戏，但没有成功，但布莱恩非常有耐心。”</p><p>虽然洛文塔尔的竞选活动迄今为止并不成功，但他认为 Insomniac Games 试图为他的角色蜘蛛侠提供一套游戏套装来安抚他。 </p><figure id="attachment_3498191" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3498191" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3498191" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-preview-2.jpg" alt="漫威蜘蛛侠 2。图片来源：Insomniac Games。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-preview-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-preview-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-preview-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-preview-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-preview-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Marvels-Spider-Man-2-preview-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3498191" class="wp-caption-text">漫威蜘蛛侠 2。图片来源：Insomniac Games。</figcaption></figure><p> “如果你预购了游戏，你就会得到阿拉克骑士套装，不知何故，我认为这是他试图安抚我的方式，”他开玩笑说。 “我确信这与我无关，但事实上他们将阿拉克骑士套装作为你可以获得的第一套套装，我觉得这是一种奉献，我喜欢它。”</p><p>洛文塔尔并不是《月光骑士》的唯一粉丝。该角色最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-interviews/oscar-isaac-interview-moon-knight-marvel-mental-health-3188620">由奥斯卡·伊萨克在漫威迪士尼+同名系列中扮演</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/moon-knight-review-oscar-isaac-3193153">我们在评论中授予了五颗星</a>。</p><p>去年，艾萨克表示该剧“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/oscar-isaac-says-theres-no-official-plans-for-moon-knight-season-two-3219212">没有正式计划</a>”制作第二季。</p><p>至于<em>漫威的《蜘蛛侠 2》</em> ，PS5 独占游戏于今天（10 月 20 日）推出，并受到评论家的热烈欢迎。关于这个话题，Intihar 最近告诉<em>NME，</em>工作室“并没有搞砸”<em>漫威蜘蛛侠</em>中粉丝们喜欢的部分。</p><p> “我们没有搞砸挥杆或战斗，”他解释道。 “我们发现了人们喜欢的东西，并寻找机会来提升他们。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/marvels-spider-man-2-peter-parker-moon-knight-yuri-lowenthal-3517769">《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》明星“试图”让月亮骑士加入游戏的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥“没完没了”的即兴表演让马丁·斯科塞斯和罗伯特·德尼罗“翻白眼” https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprios-endless-ad-libs-left-martin-scorsese-and-robert-de-niro-rolling-their-eyes-3518774?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=莱昂纳多-迪卡普里奥-无尽-即兴表演-左马丁-斯科塞斯和罗伯特-德尼罗-翻白眼Chris EdwardsFri, 20 Oct 2023 15:51:22 +0000 Film NewsNewskillersMartin Scorsese https://www.nme.com/?p=3518774 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们会告诉他：‘你不需要那种对话’”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprios-endless-ad-libs-left-martin-scorsese-and-robert-de-niro-rolling-their-eyes-3518774">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥“没完没了”的即兴表演让马丁·斯科塞斯和罗伯特·德尼罗“翻白眼”，这篇文章</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>导演表示，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/killers-of-the-flower-moon"><em>《花月杀手》</em></a>中“没完没了”的即兴表演让<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯</a>和罗伯特·德尼罗“翻白眼”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">《花月杀手》评论：马丁·斯科塞斯令人心碎的真实犯罪冷门</a></strong></li></ul><p>斯科塞斯的第 26 部电影根据 1920 年代俄克拉荷马州 60 多名美洲原住民被谋杀的真实故事改编，由德尼罗和迪卡普里奥主演，饰演一对叔叔和侄子，密谋窃取部落土地下的石油。</p><p>迪卡普里奥以在电影中即兴台词而闻名，但在拍摄这部时代作品时，这位演员显然考验了他的搭档兼导演的耐心。</p><p>斯科塞斯告诉<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2023/10/19/dicaprio-ad-libs-scorsese-de-niro-rolling-their-eyes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日电讯报》</em></a> ，他的即兴创作“无穷无尽、无穷无尽”，而“鲍勃（德尼罗）却不想说话。”</p><p>这位 80 岁的导演曾与两位演员合作拍摄过多部电影，他说：“鲍勃和我时不时地看着对方，翻白眼。我们会告诉[迪卡普里奥]：‘你不需要那种对话。’” </p><figure id="attachment_3445147" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3445147" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3445147" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270.jpg" alt="罗伯特·德尼罗和莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥的剧照，取自《花月杀手》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3445147" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·德尼罗和莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥的剧照，取自《花月杀手》。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>此前，斯科塞斯最近透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese-overhaul-killers-of-the-flower-moon-script-3516208">迪卡普里奥在剧本创作两年后要求对电影剧本进行重大修改</a>。</p><p>虽然这部电影最终是从奥塞奇部落的角度讲述的，但这并不是最初的计划。据导演称，电影的原始剧本是“从调查局特工前来调查的角度讲述的”，这引发了迪卡普里奥对剧本的质疑。</p><p>斯科塞斯告诉<a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/2023/10/14/martin-scorsese-one-has-to-take-chances-at-this-age-what-else-can-i-do/"><em>《</em><em>爱尔兰时报》</em></a> ：“里奥来找我，问我，‘这个故事的核心在哪里？’我曾与奥色治人开会并共进晚餐，我想，好吧，故事就是这样。我们认为，真正的故事不一定来自局外，而是来自俄克拉荷马州内部。”</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对该片的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">五星级评论</a>中写道：“这是斯科塞斯最重要的作品之一。 1920 年代的流行音乐、美洲原住民歌曲和罗比·罗伯逊的蓝调音乐使这部非凡的西部片更加完美，这部电影将在观众的脑海中萦绕很长一段时间。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprios-endless-ad-libs-left-martin-scorsese-and-robert-de-niro-rolling-their-eyes-3518774">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥“没完没了”的即兴表演让马丁·斯科塞斯和罗伯特·德尼罗“翻白眼”，这篇文章</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
