oblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Roblox 公司已要求其大多数远程员工每周在办公室工作三天，如果他们无法做到这一点，他们将获得遣散费。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-bryan-intihar-marvels-spider-man-2-3516664">Bryan Intihar 如何在《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》中打造电子游戏杰作</a></strong></li></ul><p>首席执行官 David Baszucki 在一封致 Roblox Corporation 员工的公开信中透露了这一消息，并补充说这并不是一个“轻率”做出的决定。</p><p>他解释说，以这种身份返回办公室是为了提高效率，而且当小组审查之类的事情亲自进行时“不会那么累人”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3471521" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3471521" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3471521 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/roblox-leak-sorry-email-thosuands-of-developers.jpg" alt="个人电脑上的“Roblox” 图片来源：Oberon Copeland @veryinformed.com 来自 Unsplash" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/roblox-leak-sorry-email-thosuands-of-developers.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/roblox-leak-sorry-email-thosuands-of-developers-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/roblox-leak-sorry-email-thosuands-of-developers-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/roblox-leak-sorry-email-thosuands-of-developers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/roblox-leak-sorry-email-thosuands-of-developers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/roblox-leak-sorry-email-thosuands-of-developers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3471521" class="wp-caption-text">个人电脑上的“Roblox” 图片来源：Oberon Copeland @veryinformed.com 来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> “虽然我相信我们将达到虚拟工作空间与物理空间一样具有吸引力、协作性和生产力的程度，但我们还没有达到这一点，”他继续说道。</p><p>并不是每个人都被要求采取行动——“需要远程的团队和角色”和“拥有利基技能或重要机构知识的个人”将不受此命令的约束。</p><p>那些受影响的人有三个月的时间来决定他们能够做什么。如果他们选择搬迁到圣马特奥办事处工作，Roblox Corporation 将以某种形式为他们提供经济支持。</p><p>如果他们选择遣散费，他们将有三个月的时间过渡自己的角色，截止日期为 2024 年 4 月 15 日。 </p><figure id="attachment_3518802" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3518802" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3518802" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/roblox-corp-asks-most-of-remote-staff-to-return-to-office-part-time-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3518802" class="wp-caption-text">坐在沙发上使用笔记本电脑的人 图片来源：Sam Lion via Pexels</figcaption></figure><p>遣散费由“个人水平和服务期限以及每个人保单上六个月的医疗保险”决定。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，Motive Studio 表示，它再次利用<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ea-invites-marvel-fans-to-help-create-iron-man-game-3518710">社区委员会来指导其新钢铁侠游戏的开发</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/roblox-corporation-issues-ultimatum-to-employees-working-from-home-3518035">Roblox 公司向在家工作的员工发出最后通牒的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
棘手的“Maxinquaye”：“我很感激，但我也看到了对我心灵造成的伤害” https://www.nme.com/news/music/tricky-interview-maxinquaye-terry-hall-mazy-massive-attack-portishead-3518756?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tricky-interview-maxinquaye-terry-hall-迷宫大规模攻击波蒂斯黑德Alex RigottiFri, 20 Oct 2023 15:18:19 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3518756 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="棘手。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位布里斯托尔偶像向 NME 讲述了他一生都在逃避的专辑，激励了 Billie Eilish，并缅怀已故的女儿 Mazy 和 The Specials 的 Terry Hall</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tricky-interview-maxinquaye-terry-hall-mazy-massive-attack-portishead-3518756">《Maxinquaye》上的 Tricky 帖子：“我确实很感激，但我也看到了对我心灵造成的伤害”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="棘手。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/TRICKY_PRESS_SHOT_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tricky">Tricky</a>接受了<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了他的首张专辑《Maxinquaye》的重新发行，并分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-specials">The Specials</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tERRY-HALL">Terry Hall</a>的回忆，并驳斥了有关与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/portishead">Portishead</a>打架的谣言。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/terry-hall-the-specials-obituary-3370063"><strong>阅读更多：特里</strong>·霍尔 (Terry Hall) 和 The Specials 如何为英国文化敲响了急需的警钟</a></li></ul><p>这位出生于布里斯托尔的艺术家（真名 Adrian Thaws）以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack 的</a>联合创始人而闻名，他与 Portishead 和 Tricky 本人一起引领了“trip-hop”场景。 1995 年，他发行了首张个人专辑“Maxinquaye”，其中由 Tricky 与当时的搭档 Martina Topley Bird 一起制作和演唱。 <em>NME</em>宣布《Maxinquaye》超越<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis 的</a>《What&#39;s The Story (Morning Glory)》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a>的《The Bends》成为年度专辑。它还获得了水星奖提名，但输给了波蒂斯黑德的《Dummy》。</p><p>回顾《Maxinquaye》留下的遗产，Tricky 说：“我确实很感激，但我也看到了它对我的心灵造成的伤害。”</p><p>据报道，这位音乐家因《Maxinquaye》而名声大噪。解冻搬到纽约以保护自己的匿名性。在洛杉矶、巴黎和柏林生活过之后，他现在居住在图卢兹。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Tricky -“克服”（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ViHiOopNTlc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这张重新发行的专辑被 Tricky 称为“轮回”，其中有五首歌曲完全由 Tricky 重写（《Aftermath》、《Strugglin》、《Pumpkin》、《Hell Is Round The Corner》和《Ponderosa》）。 《Maxinquaye (Reincarnated)》还收录了八首之前未发行的混音作品，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leftfield">Leftfield</a>的一首。</p><p> Tricky 表示，他想重写这些歌曲，因为他认为原曲听起来“过时”，并受到启发，用他的音乐演变和当前对某些曲目的感受来更新这张专辑。</p><p> “我想带他们去别的地方，”他解释道。 “这些年来我得到了如此多的爱，所以我必须付出一些努力，这是人们应得的。我非常感谢这些年来我得到的支持。”</p><p>这张专辑以 Tricky 的母亲 Maxine Quaye 的名字命名。当 Tricky 12 个月大时，她患有癫痫症并被送进精神病房。她的祖母把特里基交给她照顾。</p><p>在特里奇决定将重新发行的作品称为轮回后不久，据报道，他接到蒂珀雷里的一位表弟的电话，说他知道一个盒子里装着他和母亲唯一一张已知的照片。那个盒子是他们的曾祖母发现的，她和家人住在科罗拉多州。这张照片现在是“Maxinquaye（转世）”的封面。 “这个时机实在是太荒谬了，”索斯说。 “这是命中注定的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cwkl9QcIa0y/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 5